{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/privacy/layout,_N_T_/privacy/page,_N_T_/privacy"},"segmentPaths":["/_tree","/_full","/privacy/__PAGE__","/privacy","/_index","/_head"]},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\" class=\"geist_db8459eb-module__PZ6jEG__variable h-full antialiased\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/caa3a2e1cccd8315-s.p.0wgildi0cnwt9.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/26-vtkwx7du7u.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/0-5l55wg8eb8f.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/15orcrkp-_9ct.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/2ncdmtj91g36a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/106gf3tkm7-oi.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/turbopack-3chenhptj0c52.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1el5-48au3iai.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/1rxncug86bump.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-2X5RZVJ3WV\" as=\"script\"/><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Privacy Policy — Bridge Tutoring</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Bridge matches your child with a hand-picked tutor in Pretoria and Johannesburg. Request a tutor today and hear back within 24 hours.\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"Bridge Tutoring\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Hand-picked tutors in Pretoria &amp; Johannesburg.\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"Bridge Tutoring\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Hand-picked tutors in Pretoria &amp; Johannesburg.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.2vob68tjqpejf.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0cz1d0mv5g_q7.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col bg-white text-neutral-900\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><div class=\"flex flex-col min-h-full\"><header class=\"sticky top-0 z-50 bg-white/90 backdrop-blur border-b border-neutral-100\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex h-16 items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"text-xl font-bold tracking-tight text-teal-700\" href=\"/\">Bridge</a><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-neutral-600 hover:text-neutral-900 transition-colors px-3 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-neutral-100\" href=\"/become-tutor\">Become a tutor</a><a class=\"text-sm font-semibold bg-teal-600 text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-xl hover:bg-teal-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/request-tutor\">Find a tutor</a></nav></div></div></header><main class=\"flex-1 mx-auto max-w-3xl w-full px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16\"><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">Privacy Policy</h1><p class=\"text-sm text-neutral-400 mb-10\">Last updated: June 2026</p><div class=\"prose prose-neutral max-w-none text-neutral-700 leading-relaxed space-y-8\"><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">1. Who we are</h2><p>Bridge Tutoring (“Bridge”, “we”, “us”) operates this website. We provide a tutor-matching service for parents and students in Pretoria and Johannesburg, South Africa. We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with the Protection of Personal Information Act 4 of 2013 (POPIA).</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">2. Information we collect</h2><p>We collect information you provide directly when you:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2\"><li>Submit a tutor request (name, phone, email, child details)</li><li>Apply to become a tutor (name, contact details, qualifications, experience)</li></ul><p class=\"mt-2\">We also collect standard analytics data (pages visited, device type, approximate location) via Google Analytics 4. This data is anonymised and does not personally identify you.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">3. How we use your information</h2><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1\"><li>To match you or your child with a suitable tutor</li><li>To contact you about your request or application</li><li>To improve our service</li></ul><p class=\"mt-2\">We do not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">4. Who we share your information with</h2><p>We may share your information with the tutor we match you with, solely for the purpose of facilitating the tutoring relationship. We use Resend (email delivery) and the Meta WhatsApp Business API for internal notifications. Both services process data on our behalf and are bound by their own privacy policies.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">5. How long we keep your data</h2><p>We retain your personal information for as long as necessary to fulfil the purpose for which it was collected, or as required by law. If you would like your data deleted, please contact us.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">6. Your rights</h2><p>Under POPIA, you have the right to access, correct, or request deletion of your personal information. To exercise these rights, contact us at the address below.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">7. Cookies</h2><p>We use cookies solely for analytics purposes via Google Analytics 4. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2\">8. Contact</h2><p>For any privacy-related questions or requests, please contact us at<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:privacy@bridgetutoring.co.za\" class=\"text-teal-600 underline\">privacy@bridgetutoring.co.za</a>.</p></section></div></main><footer class=\"mt-auto border-t border-neutral-100 bg-neutral-50\"><div class=\"mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3\"><div><span class=\"text-lg font-bold text-teal-700\">Bridge</span><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-neutral-500 leading-relaxed\">Hand-picked tutors in Pretoria and Johannesburg. We do the matching — you focus on results.</p></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-3\">Get started</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-500\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/request-tutor\">Find a tutor</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/become-tutor\">Become a tutor</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-700 mb-3\">Legal</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-neutral-500\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-teal-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy policy</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"mt-10 border-t border-neutral-200 pt-6 text-xs text-neutral-400\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- -->Bridge Tutoring. All rights reserved. Pretoria &amp; Johannesburg, South Africa.</div></div></footer></div><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0-5l55wg8eb8f.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[79520,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1el5-48au3iai.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/1el5-48au3iai.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/14mrh2-p_w84d.js\\\"],\\\"d